# 🛒 Amazon Home Page Clone

A static clone of the **Amazon home page**, built using **HTML** and **CSS**. This project replicates the layout and styling of Amazon’s front page to practice front-end design skills.

## 🎯 Features
- Header with logo, search bar, and navigation links
- Product sections with images and category banners
- Responsive layout using CSS Flexbox/Grid
- Footer with useful links

## 💻 Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS

## 🚀 How to View
1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in any web browser.

## 📁 Project Structure
├── index.html
└── style.css

## 📌 Note
This is a **frontend-only** project created for learning purposes. No backend functionality (e.g., cart, login) is included.
